The paper deals with the problem of gathering a squad of autonomous robots, which is a classic problem in multi-agent systems (MAS) and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). The paper also proposes a new algorithm for this problem, which involves the coordination and control of multiple robots, making it relevant to cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also deals with the dynamics of the ring, which is a key aspect of the problem, making it relevant to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper proposes a gracefully degrading algorithm, which involves adapting to the dynamics of the system, making it relevant to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
